name: Appartement a louer centre ville
description:
Located in Fès, 2.6 km from Royal Palace Fes and 1.8 km from Fes Railway Station, Appartement a louer centre ville offers air conditioning. The property is situated 3.8 km from Batha Square, 4.3 km from Bab Bou Jeloud Fes and 4.4 km from Medersa Bouanania. Staff on-site can arrange a shuttle service.

The apartment is equipped with 1 separate bedroom, 1 bathroom, a fully equipped kitchen with a dining area and fridge, and a living room with a flat-screen TV.

Karaouiyne is 7.1 km from the apartment, while Aoua Lake is 49 km away. The nearest airport is Fès–Saïs, 14 km from Appartement a louer centre ville, and the property offers a paid airport shuttle service.

name: Hotel Mounia
description:
Located in the Ville Nouvelle district of the city, this air-conditioned hotel has a traditional Moroccan décor with Zellige and ancient engravings. It features a restaurant and a spa and a hammam.

Guest rooms are simply decorated and offer a TV with satellite channels. They each have a modern en suite bathroom with a bathtub and guests can access free Wi-Fi throughtout the property.

Breakfast is served each morning at the hotel. For other meals you can sample traditional Moroccan dishes at the Délice international restaurant, or enjoy a drink in the English-style bar.

Evening entertainment is proposed in the hotel’s nightclub “Sphinx”. Relaxation activities include a body and hair treatments.

Guests can eat in the on-site restaurant, which is open for dinner, lunch, brunch and high tea.

Guests at the apartment will be able to enjoy activities in and around Fès, like walking tours.

Batha Square is 3.5 km from Appartement ensoleillé et lumineux à proximité du centre ville, while Bab Bou Jeloud Fes is 4 km away. The nearest airport is Fès–Saïs Airport, 13 km from the accommodation.

name: Hôtel Olympic
description:
With a traditional architecture, this hotel is situated in Fes’ Medina and features air-conditioned room, a restaurant and a Moroccan-style lounge.  Fes Airport is 14 km away and the Train Station is a 14-minute walk.

Provided with free Wi-Fi access, rooms at Hôtel Olympic have a private bathroom with a shower and a balcony with a panoramic view. Decorated with handicrafts, they are also provided with a satellite TV.

A continental breakfast is offered daily and can be served in the room upon request. Guests are invited to sample the Moroccan dishes proposed by the hotel’s restaurant.

Fes Central Market is right next to the Hôtel Olympic and the Bou Inania Madrasa is a 10-minute drive. Fes Golf Club is an 11-minute drive and the thermal city of Moulay Yacoub is 22 km away.
